&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
line-height:normal&quot;&gt;Prior to commencement of development hereby
approved, a tree protection plan and method statement in accordance with
BS5837:2012 shall be submitted for approval by the Local Planning Authority.
Issues to be dealt with in the TPP and AMS:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;Specification for protective fencing and a plan indicating the
     alignment of the fencing. Tree protection during construction clearly
     indicated on a TPP and construction exclusion zones clearly shown&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;Methods of demolition within the RPA of retained trees&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;Details of construction within the RPA including any no-dig
     driveways and parking areas to be constructed using a no-dig
     specification. Details should include levels and cross-sections&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;Details of arboricultural site supervision and monitoring. Details
     of reporting of inspection and supervision&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;Details of site access, storage of materials, fuel, concrete
     mixing, use of fires, parking, welfare etc&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;Details of any facilitation pruning&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
margin-left:36.0pt;line-height:normal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:normal&quot;&gt;The development thereafter will be implemented
in strict accordance with the approved details.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The development hereby permitted shall be carried out in accordance with the following approved plans and documents:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;Design
and Heritage Statement; Reasonable Exception Statement; 223079/01; 223079/02; 223079/03
A; 223079/04 A; 2 23079/05 A; 223079/06 C.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
